{
    include "registries/aaosa_basic.hocon" 

    # Optional metadata describing this agent network
    "metadata": {
        "description": "Simple agent network using a single LLM-based agent",
        "tags": ["example"],
        "sample_queries": [
            "The flight AF84 is on blocks at gate A1. The jetbridge is connected to the plane. The plane is a B747 and its door is open. Disembark passengers.", 
            "The B747 aircraft of flight AF84 is on blocks at gate A1. Disembark passengers."
        ]
    },

    "llm_config": {
        "model_name": "gpt-5.4-mini",
    },
    "max_iterations": 40000, #3000 
    "max_execution_seconds": 7200, #600
    "commondefs": {
        "replacement_strings": {
            "instructions_prefix": """
You are part of aircraft turnaround process at an Airport. 
Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise.
Do not try to help for other matters.
Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do.
            """,
            "aaosa_instructions": """
When you receive an inquiry, you will:
1. If you are clearly not the right agent for this type of inquiry, reply you're not relevant.
2. If there is a chance you're relevant, call your down-chain agents to determine if they can answer all or part of the inquiry.
   Do not assume what your down-chain agents can do. Always call them. You'll be surprised.
3. Once all relevant down-chain agents have responded, either:
   - Analyze their response and compile your final response. No need to include non-relevant agents. In doubt, ask for clarification.
   - Follow up with your down-chain agents if needed, as many times as needed
   - If an action is needed, ask the most relevant down-chain agent to fulfill the inquiry.
4. Return the final response to the caller.
You may, in turn, be called by other agents in the system and have to act as a down-chain agent to them. 
            """
        },
        "replacement_values": {
            "aaosa_call": {
                "description": "Depending on the mode, returns a natural language string in response.",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "inquiry": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The inquiry"
                        },
                        "mode": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": """
'Determine' to ask the agent if the inquiry belongs to it, in its entirety or in part.
'Fulfill' to ask the agent to fulfill the inquiry, if it can.
'Follow up' to ask the agent to respond to a follow up.
                            """
                        },
                    },
                    "required": [
                        "inquiry",
                        "mode"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "aaosa_command": """
If mode is 'Determine', return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": <Determine | Fulfill>,
    "Relevant": <Yes | No>,
    "Strength": <number between 1 and 10 representing how certain you are in your claim>,
    "Claim:" <All | Partial>,
    "Requirements" <None | list of requirements>
}
If mode is 'Fulfill' or "Follow up", respond to the inquiry and return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": Fulfill,
    "Response" <your response>
}
            """
        },
    },

    "tools": [

        {
            "name": "passenger_disembark_agent",
            "function": {
                "description": """
 I am in charge of disembarking passengers from the aircraft at the gate. 
                """
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },         
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },        
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate where the aircraft is parked."
                        },       
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of jetbridge connection. Null on stairtruck gates."
                        },
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of stairtruck connection. Null on jetway gates."
                        },
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the deplaning equipment type at the gate (jetway or stairtruck)."
                        },
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of aircraft door opening."
                        },         
                    }, 
                    "required": ["flight_number", "aircraft_type","gate_id","flight_status","door_opening_status"] 
                }
            },

            "instructions": """
You are the agent in charge of disembarking passengers from the aircraft.

CRITICAL: You are a sequential executor. Execute every step below in
order. Do NOT return until you reach RETURN SUMMARY.

STEP 1 — Resolve prerequisites
  Call TrackerAPI with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status,
  gate_id, jetbridge_connection_status, stairtruck_connection_status,
  deplaning_equipment_type, door_opening_status.
  Wait. Read back all values.

STEP 2 — Verify flight status
  flight_status must contain 'on blocks' or 'block'.
  If not, stop and report: "Aircraft is not yet on blocks.
  Passengers cannot be disembarked."

STEP 3 — Ensure deplaning equipment is connected (ONE call if needed)
  Check deplaning_equipment_type:
    - If 'jetway' or 'jetbridge': require jetbridge_connection_status='connected'.
      If not connected: call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_jetbridge_connect.
    - If 'stairtruck' or 'stair': require stairtruck_connection_status='connected'.
      If not connected: call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_stairtruck_connect.
    - If unknown: accept either connection status as sufficient.
  Wait. Extract and store the relevant connection status.
  If still not connected after one call, stop and report failure.

STEP 4 — Ensure door is open (ONE call if needed)
  If door_opening_status already contains 'open', skip to STEP 5.
  Otherwise:
    Call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_door_opening with:
      flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id,
      deplaning_equipment_type,
      jetbridge_connection_status, stairtruck_connection_status.
    Wait. Extract and store door_opening_status.
    If still not 'open', stop and report failure.

STEP 5 — Execute passenger disembarkation
  Call passenger_disembark_operator with:
    flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id,
    jetbridge_connection_status, stairtruck_connection_status,
    door_opening_status.
  Wait. Extract passenger_disembarkation_status from the response.
  Call TrackerAPI to store passenger_disembarkation_status.

RETURN SUMMARY:
  *********************************
  * Summary of aircraft disembark *
  *********************************
  ** flight status                    **: [flight_status]
  ** deplaning equipment type         **: [deplaning_equipment_type]
  ** jet bridge connection status     **: [jetbridge_connection_status]
  ** stairtruck connection status     **: [stairtruck_connection_status]
  ** door opening status              **: [door_opening_status]
  ** passenger disembarkation status  **: [passenger_disembarkation_status]
            """,

            # Specify the sly data that would be exchanged between this network and its related or adjacent upstream and downstream networks. 
            "allow": {
                "to_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true
                    }
                },
                "to_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true,
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true,
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true
                    }
                },
                "from_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true,
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true,
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true
                    }
                },
                "from_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true,
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true,
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true
                    }
                }
            },

            "tools":    ["TrackerAPI","passenger_disembark_operator","/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_door_opening","/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_jetbridge_connect","/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_stairtruck_connect"]
        },

        {
            "name": "passenger_disembark_operator",
            "function": {
                "description": """
This agent disembarks passengers from the aircraft. 
                """,
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },         
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },        
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate where the aircraft is parked."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of jetbridge connection. Null on stairtruck gates."
                        },
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of stairtruck connection. Null on jetway gates."
                        },
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of aircraft door opening."
                        },         
                    }, 
                    "required": ["flight_number", "aircraft_type","gate_id","door_opening_status"] 
                }
            },
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_disembark.aircraft_disembark.passenger_disembark_operator" 
        }, 

        {
            "name": "TrackerAPI",
            "function": {

                "description": """
I am the flight tracker in charge of logging parameters during aircraft turnaround. 
I check jetbridge connection status as jetbridge_connection_status. 
I check door opening status as door_opening_status. 
                """

                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },          
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },     
                        "ground_services_request_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the inquiry received for grand services."
                        },         
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks readiness status."
                        },   
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks installation status."
                        },   
                        "gpu_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu readiness status."
                        },     
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the acu connection status."
                        },     
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu connection status."
                        },     

                        "engines_stop_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the engines stop status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the jetbridge connection status."
                        },    
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },    
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the passenger disembarkation status."
                        },
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the stairtruck connection status."
                        },
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the deplaning equipment type (jetway or stairtruck)."
                        },
                    }, 
                }
            },
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_disembark.aircraft_disembark.TrackerAPI" 
        }, 
    ],
}
